      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle has been preserved to an exacting standard, exhibiting showroom-quality aesthetics and uncompromising mechanical integrity. It represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a vehicle that mirrors its original factory delivery state in every measurable aspect.",
