    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I am honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it's time for a new home! This car is in absolutely stunning condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've babied it since day one, kept it tucked away in the garage, and there isn't a single scratch or dent to be found. It drives like an absolute dream and is totally ready for your next big road trip. You've gotta come see it in person, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
