    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3, a superlative example of the E46 platform. This specimen is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that delivers seamless power across the entire tachometer. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise, tactile shifts, mated to the factory-original M Variable Differential Lock. Critical subframe reinforcement has been completed to exceed OEM specifications, ensuring chassis rigidity under lateral load. The exterior retains its factory depth and luster, while the undercarriage remains free of oxidation. Mechanical updates include a comprehensive cooling system overhaul and fresh rod bearings for peace of mind. This is a turn-key machine for the purist who demands mechanical perfection and uncompromised performance dynamics.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "2022 model. Garage kept. Zero accidents. Original factory paint. Interior smells new. Full service records included.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional 2018 Porsche 718 Cayman, preserved in what can only be described as showroom condition. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen a drop of rain. The Guards Red exterior retains a deep, mirror-like luster with zero swirl marks or stone chips, protected by a full-front clear bra. Inside, the Black leather interior still carries that new-car aroma; the bolsters are firm, the stitching is pristine, and every switch operates with factory-fresh precision. Mechanically, it is flawless, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified Porsche technicians. It sits on unmarked 20-inch Carrera S wheels wrapped in fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. This is a collector-grade example for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
